## Runtime database artifacts
# The app's real SQLite database is NOT stored in this repository.
# Runtime files live under %LOCALAPPDATA%\GoogleCalendarManagement\calendar.db.
# Do not ignore the repo's `Data/` folder here: `Data/Entities`, `Data/Configurations`,
# and `Data/Migrations` are tracked C# source files, not local user data.
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal

